<!doctype html>
<html lang="ru">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>{{title}}</title>
    <style>
      :root {
        --bg: #f3f4f6;
        --card-bg: #ffffff;
        --border: #e5e7eb;
        --accent: #2563eb;
        --success: #16a34a;
        --success-soft: #dcfce7;
        --text-main: #111827;
        --text-muted: #6b7280;
        --text-soft: #9ca3af;
        --radius-lg: 22px;
        --radius-md: 14px;
        color-scheme: light;
      }

      * {
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 6px;
        background: var(--bg);
        font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
        font-size: 14px;
        color: var(--text-main);
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
      }

      .mono {
        font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, "Liberation Mono", "Courier New", monospace;
      }

      .receipt-wrapper {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 428px;
      }

      .receipt-card {
        background: var(--card-bg);
        border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
        box-shadow:
          0 18px 45px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.16),
          0 0 0 1px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.02);
        overflow: hidden;
      }

      .receipt-header {
        padding: 18px 20px 14px;
        background: linear-gradient(145deg, #f9fafb 0%, #ffffff 60%, #eef2ff 100%);
        border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.25);
      }

      .header-top {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: flex-start;
        gap: 12px;
      }

      .logo-mark {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 10px;
      }

      .logo-icon {
        width: 30px;
        height: 30px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e3a8a 0%, #1e40af 50%, #1e293b 100%);
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        color: #ffffff;
        font-size: 14px;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: -0.02em;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(30, 58, 138, 0.3);
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
      }

      .logo-icon::before {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        width: 40%;
        height: 100%;
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(147, 197, 253, 0.4), transparent);
      }

      .logo-text {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 0;
      }

      .logo-text-main {
        font-size: 14px;
        font-weight: 500;
        letter-spacing: 0.01em;
        color: #0f172a;
      }

      .logo-text-sub {
        font-size: 10px;
        color: var(--text-muted);
      }

      .status-badge {
        padding: 4px 10px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: var(--success-soft);
        color: var(--success);
        font-size: 11px;
        font-weight: 600;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.09em;
        white-space: nowrap;
      }

      .header-meta {
        margin-top: 22px;
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.4fr) minmax(0, 1fr);
        align-items: end;
        gap: 10px;
      }

      .header-meta > div:first-child .meta-note {
        display: none;
      }

      .meta-label {
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.14em;
        font-size: 10px;
        color: var(--text-soft);
        margin-bottom: 3px;
      }

      .meta-value {
        font-size: 13px;
        color: var(--text-main);
      }

      .meta-note {
        font-size: 11px;
        color: var(--text-muted);
      }

      .meta-right {
        text-align: right;
      }

      .meta-serial {
        font-size: 18px;
        font-weight: 600;
      }

      .receipt-body {
        padding: 14px 20px 18px;
      }

      .section {
        border-radius: var(--radius-md);
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        padding: 12px 12px 10px;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }

      .field-label {
        font-size: 11px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.12em;
        color: var(--text-soft);
        margin-bottom: 3px;
      }

      .field-value {
        font-size: 14px;
        color: var(--text-main);
      }

      .field-value-muted {
        font-size: 12px;
        color: var(--text-muted);
        margin-top: 2px;
      }

      .services-title {
        font-size: 10px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.16em;
        color: var(--text-soft);
        margin-bottom: 8px;
      }

      .services-header-row {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        font-size: 10px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.16em;
        color: var(--text-soft);
        padding-bottom: 6px;
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      }

      .services-header-right {
        display: flex;
        gap: 18px;
      }

      .service-row {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        padding: 8px 0;
        border-bottom: 1px dashed #e5e7eb;
        gap: 12px;
      }

      .service-main {
        flex: 1 1 auto;
        min-width: 0;
      }

      .service-name {
        font-size: 16px;
        color: var(--text-main);
      }

      .service-meta {
        margin-top: 3px;
        font-size: 11px;
        color: var(--text-muted);
      }

      .service-right {
        flex: 0 0 auto;
        text-align: right;
        font-size: 13px;
        white-space: nowrap;
      }

      .service-right-content {
        display: flex;
        gap: 18px;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: flex-end;
      }

      .service-right-content > * {
        min-width: 60px;
        text-align: right;
      }

      .service-qty {
        font-size: 16px;
        color: var(--text-muted);
      }

      .summary-block {
        margin-top: 6px;
        padding-top: 8px;
        border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: flex-end;
        gap: 10px;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
      }

      .summary-label {
        font-size: 11px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.16em;
        color: var(--text-soft);
      }

      .summary-amount {
        font-size: 20px;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #0f172a;
      }

      .summary-note {
        margin-top: 2px;
        font-size: 11px;
        color: var(--text-muted);
      }

      .pay-form-block {
        margin-top: 10px;
      }

      .signature-line {
        margin-top: 5px;
        padding-bottom: 4px;
        border-bottom: 1px dashed #d1d5db;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: space-between;
        gap: 10px;
      }

      .signature-title {
        font-size: 11px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.16em;
        color: var(--text-soft);
      }

      .signature-name {
        font-size: 13px;
        color: var(--text-main);
      }

      .signature-role {
        font-size: 11px;
        color: var(--text-muted);
        margin-top: 2px;
      }

      .signature-placeholder {
        font-size: 12px;
        color: var(--text-soft);
        white-space: nowrap;
      }

      .signature-note {
        margin-top: 4px;
        font-size: 11px;
        color: var(--text-muted);
      }

      .footer-note {
        border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        background: #f9fafb;
        padding: 10px 10px 14px;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 10px;
        color: var(--text-soft);
      }

      @media (max-width: 480px) {
        .receipt-card {
          border-radius: 18px;
        }

        .receipt-header,
        .receipt-body {
          padding-inline: 12px;
        }

        .section {
          padding-inline: 9px;
        }

        .header-meta {
          grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr);
        }

        .summary-block {
          align-items: flex-start;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="receipt-wrapper">
      <div class="receipt-card">
        <div class="receipt-header">
          <div class="header-top">
            <div class="logo-mark">
              <div class="logo-icon">KB</div>
              <div class="logo-text">
                <div class="logo-text-main">Квитанатор</div>
                <div class="logo-text-sub">Внутренние квитанции для ИП</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="status-badge">Оплата получена</div>
          </div>

          <div class="header-meta">
            <div>
              <div class="meta-label">Документ</div>
              <div class="meta-value meta-serial">{{title}}</div>
              <div class="meta-note">Внутренний документ для учёта оплаты услуги</div>
            </div>
            <div class="meta-right">
              <div class="meta-label">Номер</div>
              <div class="meta-value meta-serial">№ {{receiptNumber}}</div>
              <div class="meta-note">от <span class="mono">{{createdAt}}</span></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="receipt-body">
          <div class="section">
            <div class="field-label">Индивидуальный предприниматель</div>
            <div class="field-value">{{ipFullName}}</div>
            <div class="field-value field-value-muted mono">ИНН: {{inn}}</div>
          </div>

          <div class="section">
            <div class="field-label">Адрес осуществления расчёта</div>
            <div class="field-value">{{address}}</div>
          </div>

          <div class="section">
            <div class="services-title">Услуги</div>

            <div class="services-header-row">
              <div>Наименование услуги</div>
              <div class="services-header-right">
                <span>Кол-во</span>
                <span>Сумма, ₽</span>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="service-row">
              <div class="service-main">
                <div class="service-name">{{serviceTitle}}</div>
                <div class="service-meta">Оказанная услуга</div>
              </div>
              <div class="service-right">
                <div class="service-right-content">
                  <div class="service-qty">1 усл.</div>
                  <div class="mono">{{amount}}</div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="summary-block">
              <div>
                <div class="summary-label">Итого к оплате</div>
                <div class="summary-note">Сумма принята и зафиксирована во внутреннем учёте операций</div>
              </div>
              <div class="summary-amount mono">{{amount}} ₽</div>
            </div>

            <div class="pay-form-block">
              <div class="field-label">Форма расчёта</div>
              <div class="field-value">{{paymentMethodLabel}}</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="section">
            <div class="signature-title">Лицо, осуществившее расчёт</div>
            <div class="signature-line">
              <div>
                <div class="signature-name">{{ipFullName}}</div>
                <div class="signature-role">Индивидуальный предприниматель</div>
              </div>
              <div class="signature-placeholder">____________</div>
            </div>
            <div class="signature-note">
              Подпись не требуется при формировании квитанции в электронной форме.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="footer-note">Сформировано сервисом «Квитанатор»</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
